00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:47.220
So it has a lot of different
nooks and crannies,

00:02:47.220 --> 00:02:49.990
not all of which
we'll get into today.

00:02:49.990 --> 00:02:52.870
Also, because it's about
fundamental human motivation,

00:02:52.870 --> 00:02:55.330
it travels to a lot
